      "content": "i get that, but i dont really have time to go to the doctor right now and get bloodwork done. i've seen people in wellness forums saying that these high doses are totally fine if you just do them for a few weeks to \"load up\" your levels. if i just do it for like 2 weeks and then drop back down to a normal dose, is that really gonna hurt me? it seems like a lot faster than waiting for an appointment.",
